# 3. Optionally change POSTGRES_PASSWORD for added security

# For production deployment:
# 1. NEVER commit .env file to version control
# 2. SET a persistent SECRET_KEY to avoid invalidating sessions on restart
# 3. Use environment-specific secret management:
#    - AWS Secrets Manager
#    - HashiCorp Vault
